workflow Review Flowline UI Changes for Bugs
runner codex

agent review-main
title Review src/main.coil
prompt Review \`src/main.coil\` for bugs related to flowline UI changes. Examine the application state machine, input handling, layout, and rendering. Identify potential issues, logic errors, UI glitches, and regressions. Output a list of findings.
after none

agent review-native
title Review src/native.coil
prompt Review \`src/native.coil\` for bugs related to flowline UI changes. Examine native widget bindings, text rendering, layout, and integration with the application. Identify potential issues, misalignments, and rendering bugs. Output a list of findings.
after none

agent merge-findings
title Merge findings into risk list
prompt Combine the two review reports into a single risk list. Remove duplicate issues, merge related observations, and prioritize by severity. Produce a concise, actionable list of bugs and risks for human review.
after review-main, review-native

approval approve-risks
title Human approval of risk list
after merge-findings
